{"tid":1836440,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新華社：中美專家合作研發新型冠狀病毒疫苗","createTime":"2020-01-23T08:07:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T09:42:01.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"48b2c4f37f89c6649cc2cb9d7b1e9de354366396","tid":1836440,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T08:07:27.000Z","msg":"新華社：中美專家合作研發新型冠狀病毒疫苗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504428-20200123.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504428-20200123.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp8dEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=ba3663dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504428-20200123.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=19a3814f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504428-20200123.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n新華社引述美國醫學專家表示，正與中國專家合作研發針對新型冠狀病毒的疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n這名休斯敦貝勒醫學院教授說，貝勒醫學院正在與美國得克薩斯大學、紐約血液中心，以及上海復旦大學合作開發疫苗，但疫苗研發需要時間。<br />\n<br />\n另外，美國傳媒報道，美國國家衛生研究院亦正在研究針對新型冠狀病毒的疫苗，預計幾個月後可以進行第一階段臨床試驗，可能一年後才會有疫苗進入市場。"},{"pid":"35503ef1d5b119197858b205afa2bbd80595b509","tid":1836440,"uid":285371,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T08:08:16.000Z","msg":"唔洗急，慢慢黎"},{"pid":"cd1aeee5f8d886ca210a582a491d7d47469b9bb1","tid":1836440,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T08:09:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3e530fdd2e86cea9afd4df441be64797c76f03f","tid":1836440,"uid":243677,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T08:09:42.000Z","msg":"有事就合作 <br />\n冇事就外國勢力 說三道四 干涉內政"},{"pid":"c3de5b596fc48da3240f23402f5c04be8a5ce264","tid":1836440,"uid":103230,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T08:10:29.000Z","msg":"美帝又干預內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},